import React from 'react'

const UserProfilePage = () => {
    return (
        <Container >
            <Row className='py-3'>
                <Col sm="3" xs="3" md="2">
                    <UserSideBar />
                </Col>

                <Col sm="9" xs="9" md="10">
                <UserEditAddress />
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default UserProfilePage
